{"tid":651364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5月3日軍史上的今天】「尼米茲號」航艦服役","createTime":"2018-05-03T05:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T08:56:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16904c24bc8e8f9b4520fbae84650b347e916082","tid":651364,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"1975年5月3日，「尼米茲號」航艦（CVN 68）服役，開啟美國海軍的「尼米茲時代」&mdash;目前美國海軍現役航空母艦，幾乎全是「尼米茲級」。<br />\n<br />\n排水量超過10萬噸的「尼米茲號」是美國海軍的第二代核動力航空母艦，可搭載超過80架各式艦載機，服役至今曾參與「鷹爪行動」、利比亞衝突、轟炸貝魯特、波斯灣戰爭、美伊戰爭，以及阿富汗「持久自由行動」等。該艦是美國首艘在服役後回廠更換核燃料的航艦，也是美軍最新銳戰機F-35C首次登上的航艦。<br />\n<br />\n從1975年「尼米茲號」到2009年「布希號」為止，美軍共建造10艘「尼米茲級」，打造美國海軍的「尼米茲時代」。「年資」最老的「尼米茲號」預計服役50年，未來將被「福特級」2號艦「甘迺迪號」（CVN 79）取代。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/5%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E5%B0%BC%E7%B1%B3%E8%8C%B2%E8%99%9F-%E8%88%AA%E8%89%A6%E6%9C%8D%E5%BD%B9-160000269.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F5%25E6%259C%25883%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E8%258C%25B2%25E8%2599%259F-%25E8%2588%25AA%25E8%2589%25A6%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%25BD%25B9-160000269.html&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BSzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=14c37467\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/5%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E5%B0%BC%E7%B1%B3%E8%8C%B2%E8%99%9F-%E8%88%AA%E8%89%A6%E6%9C%8D%E5%BD%B9-160000269.html</a>"},{"pid":"be795249719779137e777c6184bea571606082a8","tid":651364,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002d1396ad7c38e78ee8b112454bffee665beefe","tid":651364,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"中國仲勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2367ad80a91b46262d043dff22d764c296ee3b75","tid":651364,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:54:26.000Z","msg":"尼米茲號原來都就快退役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7476691c51cd61ec0745029d14f98f38eb5ead39","tid":651364,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"Nimitz 1975年<br />\nLiaoning 1985年；翻新2012年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：中國或成最大贏家<br />\n<br />\n原因：隻野年份新啲<br />\n<br />\n完。"}]}